# **FIELDS‑IQ — HOMEPAGE DESIGN (Hybrid Style)**

## **1. Brand Tone**
- Clean  
- Minimal  
- Confident  
- Operational  
- Slightly mysterious  
- Platform‑level, not feature‑level  

Think:  
**Apple’s clarity + Vercel’s modernity + ServiceTitan’s groundedness.**

---

# **2. Hero Section**

## **Headline**
**Intelligence for the Real World of Field Operations**

## **Sub‑headline**
Smarter workflows for technicians, operators, and multi‑location businesses — built for speed, trust, and clarity.

## **Primary CTA**
**Get Started**

## **Secondary CTA**
**Learn More**

## **Visual**
A clean abstract visualization — not a product screenshot yet.  
Something like:

- Subtle geometric shapes  
- Light gradients  
- A sense of structure and flow  
- No UI until your product is ready  

This keeps the homepage premium and future‑proof.

---

# **3. Value Proposition Section**

## **Section Title**
Built for the people who keep the world running

## **Three Pillars**
### **1. Technician‑Ready**
Fast, intuitive workflows designed for the realities of field work.

### **2. Operator‑Focused**
Clear visibility, consistent processes, and smarter decision‑making.

### **3. Multi‑Location Friendly**
Built to scale across stores, regions, and entire networks.

This hints at your multi‑industry ambition without revealing the empire.

---

# **4. Platform Section (Soft Reveal)**

## **Section Title**
A smarter foundation for field operations

## **Description**
Fields‑IQ brings together workflows, intelligence, and real‑world context into a single, modern platform.  
Simple to start. Powerful as you grow.

## **Three Modules (High-Level Only)**
- **Workflows** — guided, consistent, and fast  
- **Intelligence** — context‑aware insights  
- **Connectivity** — technicians, operators, and locations in sync  

This signals platform‑level thinking without exposing CFA or IRE.

---

# **5. Social Proof (Lightweight)**

## **Section Title**
Trusted by technicians and operators across industries

No logos yet — you don’t need them.  
Just a simple line builds trust without overclaiming.

---

# **6. CTA Section**

## **Headline**
Start with a smarter foundation

## **CTA Button**
**Get Started**

---

# **7. Footer**
- Privacy  
- Terms  
- Support  
- Contact  

Clean and minimal.

---

# **VISUAL DIRECTION**
- White or very light background  
- Black or charcoal typography  
- One accent color (Fields‑IQ blue or green)  
- Subtle gradients  
- Soft shadows  
- Rounded corners (not too playful)  
- Plenty of whitespace  
- No product screenshots yet  
- No clutter  

This makes Fields‑IQ feel premium and credible.

---

# **NEXT.JS HOMEPAGE CODE (Drop‑in Ready)**  
This assumes a standard Next.js project with `/pages/index.js`.

```jsx
export default function Home() {
  return (
    <div style={{ fontFamily: "Inter, sans-serif" }}>
      {/* Hero Section */}
      <section style={{ padding: "120px 24px", textAlign: "center" }}>
        <h1 style={{ fontSize: "48px", fontWeight: "600", marginBottom: "20px" }}>
          Intelligence for the Real World of Field Operations
        </h1>
        <p style={{ fontSize: "20px", color: "#555", maxWidth: "640px", margin: "0 auto 40px" }}>
          Smarter workflows for technicians, operators, and multi‑location businesses — built for speed, trust, and clarity.
        </p>
        <div>
          <a href="/get-started" style={{
            padding: "14px 28px",
            background: "#000",
            color: "#fff",
            borderRadius: "8px",
            marginRight: "12px",
            textDecoration: "none"
          }}>
            Get Started
          </a>
          <a href="/learn-more" style={{
            padding: "14px 28px",
            border: "1px solid #000",
            borderRadius: "8px",
            textDecoration: "none",
            color: "#000"
          }}>
            Learn More
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Value Proposition */}
      <section style={{ padding: "80px 24px", background: "#fafafa" }}>
        <h2 style={{ textAlign: "center", fontSize: "32px", marginBottom: "40px" }}>
          Built for the people who keep the world running
        </h2>

        <div style={{
          display: "flex",
          maxWidth: "1000px",
          margin: "0 auto",
          gap: "40px",
          flexWrap: "wrap",
          justifyContent: "center"
        }}>
          <ValueCard title="Technician‑Ready" text="Fast, intuitive workflows designed for the realities of field work." />
          <ValueCard title="Operator‑Focused" text="Clear visibility, consistent processes, and smarter decision‑making." />
          <ValueCard title="Multi‑Location Friendly" text="Built to scale across stores, regions, and entire networks." />
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Platform Section */}
      <section style={{ padding: "80px 24px" }}>
        <h2 style={{ textAlign: "center", fontSize: "32px", marginBottom: "20px" }}>
          A smarter foundation for field operations
        </h2>
        <p style={{ textAlign: "center", maxWidth: "640px", margin: "0 auto 40px", color: "#555" }}>
          Fields‑IQ brings together workflows, intelligence, and real‑world context into a single, modern platform.
          Simple to start. Powerful as you grow.
        </p>

        <div style={{
          display: "flex",
          maxWidth: "1000px",
          margin: "0 auto",
          gap: "40px",
          flexWrap: "wrap",
          justifyContent: "center"
        }}>
          <ValueCard title="Workflows" text="Guided, consistent, and fast." />
          <ValueCard title="Intelligence" text="Context‑aware insights." />
          <ValueCard title="Connectivity" text="Technicians, operators, and locations in sync." />
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* CTA Section */}
      <section style={{ padding: "100px 24px", textAlign: "center", background: "#fafafa" }}>
        <h2 style={{ fontSize: "36px", marginBottom: "20px" }}>
          Start with a smarter foundation
        </h2>
        <a href="/get-started" style={{
          padding: "16px 32px",
          background: "#000",
          color: "#fff",
          borderRadius: "8px",
          textDecoration: "none"
        }}>
          Get Started
        </a>
      </section>

      {/* Footer */}
      <footer style={{ padding: "40px 24px", textAlign: "center", color: "#777" }}>
        <a href="/privacy" style={{ margin: "0 12px" }}>Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms" style={{ margin: "0 12px" }}>Terms</a>
        <a href="/support" style={{ margin: "0 12px" }}>Support</a>
        <a href="/contact" style={{ margin: "0 12px" }}>Contact</a>
      </footer>
    </div>
  );
}

function ValueCard({ title, text }) {
  return (
    <div style={{
      width: "280px",
      padding: "24px",
      background: "#fff",
      borderRadius: "12px",
      boxShadow: "0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)"
    }}>
      <h3 style={{ fontSize: "20px", marginBottom: "12px" }}>{title}</h3>
      <p style={{ color: "#555" }}>{text}</p>
    </div>
  );
}
```

This is clean, modern, and deploy‑ready.

